OL,3,C'One of UK's finest' collections of
OL,4,CStar Wars memorabilia comes to
OL,5,CYorkshire
OL,7,FA new summer long exhibition of
OL,8,Fclassic Star Wars memorabilia has gone
OL,9,Fon display in an East Yorkshire town.
OL,11,F'May the toys be with you' opened on 6
OL,12,FJune and runs until Saturday 29 August
OL,13,Fat Beverley Art Gallery and displays a
OL,14,Fcollections of vintage Star Wars toys
OL,15,Fand original cinema posters, from the
OL,16,Foriginal trilogy released from 1977 to
OL,17,F1985.
OL,19,FThe collection has taken owner Matt
OL,20,FFox almost 50 years to collate.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
