PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780765560
OL,3,C'One of UK's finest' collections of
OL,4,CStar Wars memorabilia comes to
OL,5,CYorkshire
OL,7,FHe said: "I encountered Star Wars as a
OL,8,Fwide-eyed five year old on my very
OL,9,Ffirst outing to a cinema, and my first
OL,10,Ffigure (Darth Vader) was purchased
OL,11,Fthat same day.
OL,13,F"Now, I'm an adult collector, but I
OL,14,Fdon't think I've ever really lost that
OL,15,Fwide-eyed joy when acquiring new
OL,16,Fpieces for my collection.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780765560
OL,3,C'One of UK's finest' collections of
OL,4,CStar Wars memorabilia comes to
OL,5,CYorkshire
OL,7,F"I still remember the pungent vinyl
OL,8,Fsmell from the plastic as I opened my
OL,9,Ffirst figure and on the back of each
OL,10,Fcard you can see all the other figures
OL,11,Favailable in the toy line and it says
OL,12,F'collect them all' and I've been
OL,13,Ftrying to obey that simple command to
OL,14,Fthis day."
OL,16,F"You can take any design from the
OL,17,Fmovie and it's become iconic.
OL,19,F''I am very pleased to be able to
OL,20,Fshare the collection with everyone who
OL,21,Fcomes to the exhibition.''
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780765560
OL,3,C'One of UK's finest' collections of
OL,4,CStar Wars memorabilia comes to
OL,5,CYorkshire
OL,7,FThe curator of the gallery Hannah
OL,8,FWilletts hopes the exhibition will
OL,9,Fhave wide appeal. She said: "you don't
OL,10,Fhave to be a super Star Wars fan for
OL,11,Fthis exhibition.
OL,13,F"It's about storytelling. It's about
OL,14,Fdesign. It's about creativity. This is
OL,15,Fa cultural phenomenon.
OL,17,F"I think it's really intergenerational
OL,18,Fit has appeal for people who grew up
OL,19,Fwith these toys but also people who
OL,20,Fare totally new to them."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
