PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780765560
OL,3,C'One of UK's finest' collections of
OL,4,CStar Wars memorabilia comes to
OL,5,CYorkshire
OL,7,FWhen the first Star Wars film hit
OL,8,Fscreens in 1977 it broke box office
OL,9,Frecords and sustained it's success
OL,10,Fwith a merchandising line which sold
OL,11,Fan estimated 300 million action
OL,12,Ffigures within the first decade.
OL,14,FThe whole film franchise, including
OL,15,Fmodern additions, has grossed more
OL,16,Fthan 10 billion dollars worldwide.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
