PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780765560
OL,3,C'One of UK's finest' collections of
OL,4,CStar Wars memorabilia comes to
OL,5,CYorkshire
OL,7,FAs part of the display in Beverley
OL,8,Fpeople will be able to learn about the
OL,9,Fphysics of Star Wars from Dr Gareth
OL,10,FFew from the University of Hull
OL,11,Fphysics department.
OL,13,FHe said: "Star Wars being so iconic is
OL,14,Fa really great way for us to try and
OL,15,Fbring to the public, some of the
OL,16,Frecent advances in physics that might
OL,17,Fmake some of the technologies you see
OL,18,Fin the films come to life."
OL,20,FDr Gareth Few is due to host a drop-in
OL,21,Fsection on Saturday 25 July.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
